title: Ep 53: Peanut Butter and Jellies
description: Jealousy and Envy - did you know they're different? Well they are and I explain it all. I also admit to being a horribly jealous 20 year old - so embarrassing...Jealousy and envy are two feelings that are so shameful and dark and that's why we are gonna get deep on them, bros!
author: nadav@ymhstudios.com (Christina Pazsitzky)
